# 18. Inheritance Example

### Animal.java

```java
class Animal {

    void makeSound() {
        System.out.println("Animal makes a sound");
    }
}
```

### Dog.java

```java
class Dog extends Animal {

    @Override
    void makeSound() {
        System.out.println("Bark");
    }
}
```

### Main.java

```java
public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Animal animal = new Animal();
        Dog dog = new Dog();

        animal.makeSound();
        dog.makeSound();
    }
}
```

### Sample Output

```text
Animal makes a sound
Bark
```

